---
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="blob blob-1"></div>
  <div class="blob blob-2"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      🎉 Nuevas webs para 2026 — Aprovecha la subvención del Kit Digital
    </div>

    <h1>
      Tu negocio merece<br />
      una web que <span class="squiggle-wrap"><em>trabaje</em><svg class="squiggle" viewBox="0 0 220 12" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2,9 C18,3 34,3 50,9 C66,15 82,15 98,9 C114,3 130,3 146,9 C162,15 178,15 194,9 C206,4 214,3 218,5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span><br />
      mientras tú duermes
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-sub">
      Diseñamos y desarrollamos webs profesionales para negocios reales.<br />
      Sin complicaciones. Con resultados. Y sí, subvencionable hasta el 100%.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#planes" class="btn-primary">Ver planes →</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/34600000000" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-secondary">
        💬 Hablar con nosotros
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-img">
    <img src="/images/hero-character.webp" alt="Diseño web profesional" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 48px;
  padding: 120px 8% 80px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: #ffffff;
}

.hero-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: left;
  z-index: 2;
}

.hero-img {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  z-index: 1;
}
.hero-img img {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 520px;
  height: auto;
}

.blob {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(90px);
  opacity: 0.12;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.blob-1 { width: 520px; height: 520px; background: var(--purple); top: -120px; right: -100px; }
.blob-2 { width: 420px; height: 420px; background: var(--orange);  bottom: -60px; left: -90px; }

.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: var(--orange-light);
  border: 1px solid #FFD4A8;
  color: var(--orange);
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 6px 16px;
  border-radius: 100px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
  width: fit-content;
}
.hero-badge::before {
  content: '';
  width: 7px;
  height: 7px;
  background: var(--orange);
  border-radius: 50%;
}

h1 {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--dark);
  max-width: 820px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.1s ease both;
}

/* ── SQUIGGLE (fly.io style) ── */
.squiggle-wrap {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  color: var(--purple);
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.squiggle-wrap em {
  font-style: italic;
  display: inline-block;
  transform: rotate(-2deg);
  transform-origin: center bottom;
}

.squiggle {
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  bottom: -0.18em;
  width: 100%;
  height: 0.35em;
  color: var(--orange);
  stroke-dasharray: 260;
  stroke-dashoffset: 260;
  animation: squiggleDraw 0.7s 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) forwards;
  overflow: visible;
}

@keyframes squiggleDraw {
  to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
}

h1:hover .squiggle {
  stroke-dashoffset: 260;
  animation: squiggleDraw 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) forwards;
}

.hero-sub {
  margin-top: 24px;
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  max-width: 560px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.2s ease both;
}

.hero-btns {
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 36px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.3s ease both;
}

@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* Tablet: reducir padding y fuente pero mantener 2 columnas */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .hero {
    padding: 100px 5% 60px;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem);
  }
}

/* Móvil: una sola columna, imagen debajo */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .hero {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    padding: 80px 5% 48px;
    gap: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-btns {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-img img {
    max-width: 280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: block;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 2.8rem);
  }
}
</style>
